att(pro60, pro2).  % [rebuttal] conf=95 — B's claim that life is sacred directly opposes A's conclusion to enforce the death penalty.
att(con211, pro2).  % [rebuttal] conf=92 — B argues the legal system's inequality makes the death penalty unjust, directly contradicting A's call for enforcement.
